---
title: Salsa-Topped Chicken Breasts with Jewelled Rice and Crispy Tortilla Topping
description: Chips for dinner?! We say 'yes'! Our enchilada spice blend brings toasty tortilla chips to the next level to create the perfect garnish for this chicken and rice dish. Rice dotted with peppers and corn is topped with  chicken smothered in mild salsa. A garnish of green onions and crushed chips makes this dinner a texture bomb!
